ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Directing the Incorporation of a Subsidiary by Canada Development Investment Corporation
PrecisOrder directing CANADA GROWTH FUND INC. to take such steps as are necessary to IMPLEMENT ITS MANDATE in accordance with any Statement of Priorities and Accountabilities, as may be issued by the Minister of Finance, in order to enable the government to establish priorities and accountabilities for this new Crown corporation.
